{"tid":2045962,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［唔再同你掟石仔］網傳解放軍中印邊境遭爆頭被俘","createTime":"2020-06-01T06:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T06:30:12.000Z","uid":24814,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a5772d756f37af4f31caf4efa139c7e95210c64f","tid":2045962,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:19:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200531/43GGUW77ALZU474TE2TOCHQAO4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200531%2F43GGUW77ALZU474TE2TOCHQAO4%2F&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGre6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=57a3d330\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200531%2F43GGUW77ALZU474TE2TOCHQAO4%2F&h=04370db9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200531/43GGUW77ALZU474TE2TOCHQAO4/</a><br />\n中國近日頻頻在國際展現軍事野心，上月在南海撞沉一艘越南漁船後，本月稍早又在印度邊境和印軍發生衝突。中國最近流傳一段網路影片，其中一名疑似解放軍人被印度軍人打得頭破血流並加以「俘虜」。有專家看了影片後認為，這段畫面真實性頗高，而中共建政以後也從未見過中印雙方出現如此對峙場面。<br />\n<br />\n（蘋果貼一段 自己入去睇）"},{"pid":"108ba9c847ad84ba3bb0e8216099386bd464b651","tid":2045962,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:22:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R7qjRVj2BbM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DR7qjRVj2BbM&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGre6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=d19dce30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R7qjRVj2BbM</a>"},{"pid":"8befc76b6e72da008d10f11e8bc4ae3de68d1e88","tid":2045962,"uid":24814,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QhD28hM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQhD28hM.jpg&h=d62edf1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4918a2caf0c17ba7d77411346d9b7e639de707c5","tid":2045962,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":